Mr. Foehr was previously employed as Senior Vice President-Technical Operations by Connetics Corp., Chief Scientific Officer-Dermatology & VP by GlaxoSmithKline LLC, and Senior VP-Global Research & Development Operations by Stiefel Research Institute, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Santa Clara University.



