Insider Activity


Individual




Matthew W. Foehr



Mr. Matthew W. Foehr is President & Chief Operating Officer at Ligand Pharmaceuticals, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Ritter Pharmaceuticals, Inc. and Viking Therapeutics, Inc. Mr. Foehr was previously employed as Senior Vice President-Technical Operations by Connetics Corp., Chief Scientific Officer-Dermatology & VP by GlaxoSmithKline LLC, and Senior VP-Global Research & Development Operations by Stiefel Research Institute, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Santa Clara University.



